text: Zuzanna Herasimowicz (born 7 July 2002) is a Polish swimmer. She competed in the women's 200 metre backstroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female backstroke swimmers
